  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de gstreamer-vaapi</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>gstreamer-vaapi</application> executando os seguintes
comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

meson  --prefix=/usr       \
       --buildtype=release \
       -Dpackage-origin=https://www.linuxfromscratch.org/blfs/view/&blfs-version;/ &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>


    <para>
      This package does not come with a vi working test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

